---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html>
	<head>
		<BaseHead
			title="PGP Key Fingerprints"
			description="GPG/PGP 公钥指纹与下载地址，用于核验签名与加密通信。"
		/>
		<style>
			:global(body) {
				background-size: 100% 0px;
			}

			main {
				display: grid;
				gap: 1.5rem;
			}
			.lead {
				margin: 0;
				color: rgb(var(--gray));
			}
			.card {
				min-width: 0;
				border: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
				border-radius: 12px;
				padding: 1rem;
				background: rgb(var(--surface));
			}
			.card h2 {
				margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
			}
			.meta {
				margin: 0.2rem 0;
				color: rgb(var(--gray));
				font-size: 0.95rem;
			}
			.fingerprint {
				display: inline-block;
				max-width: 100%;
				font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas,
					"Liberation Mono", "Courier New", monospace;
				font-size: 1rem;
				line-height: 1.5;
				word-break: break-word;
				overflow-wrap: anywhere;
				padding: 0.5rem 0.6rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				background: rgb(var(--gray-light));
				color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
			}
			.links {
				display: flex;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				gap: 0.6rem;
				margin-top: 0.75rem;
			}
			.links a {
				display: inline-block;
				text-decoration: none;
				padding: 0.35rem 0.65rem;
				border-radius: 999px;
				border: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
			}
			.links a:hover {
				border-color: var(--accent);
			}
			code {
				font-size: 0.92rem;
			}
			pre {
				max-width: 100%;
				min-width: 0;
				box-sizing: border-box;
				overflow-x: auto;
				-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
			}
			@media (max-width: 720px) {
				main {
					gap: 1rem;
				}
				.card {
					padding: 0.85rem;
					border-radius: 10px;
				}
				.fingerprint {
					display: block;
					font-size: 0.9rem;
					line-height: 1.45;
				}
				.links a {
					padding: 0.45rem 0.7rem;
				}
				pre {
					padding: 1rem;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section>
				<h1>PGP 公钥核验</h1>
				<p class="lead">
					公钥已发布到密钥服务器。请以本页面公布的指纹为准核对签名。仅在指纹完全一致时信任该公钥。
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="card" aria-labelledby="primary-key">
				<h2 id="primary-key">公开密钥</h2>
				<p class="meta">Key ID: DDC9F70191CA14A3 (ed25519)</p>
				<p class="meta">创建时间: 2025-10-19</p>
				<p class="meta">UID: gujial &lt;gujial@gujial.cc&gt; 等</p>
				<p class="fingerprint">221D 9DAD C996 6EF9 4D67 00F0 DDC9 F701 91CA 14A3</p>
				<div class="links">
					<a href="/keys/gujial-2025.asc">下载 ASCII 公钥</a>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="card" aria-labelledby="verify-commands">
				<h2 id="verify-commands">核验命令示例</h2>
				<pre><code>curl -fsS https://gujial.cc/keys/gujial-2025.asc | gpg --import
gpg --fingerprint DDC9F70191CA14A3
</code></pre>
				<p class="meta">若输出指纹与本页不一致，请不要使用该公钥。</p>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
